could cause six extra cases of cancer for every million people a 
figure later reduced to one additional case 
lappe said in an interview with the los angeles times that his 
findings indicated the health risk from malathion spraying is six 
times greater than what the report officially concluded he said he 
resigned in 1981 because of the changes 
the public has been ramrodded into accepting this without 
