bush failed to demonstrate the political will necessary to make 
the united states a leader in the effort to prevent global 
warming 
but tom lambrix head of the global climate coalition an 
industry group called bushs view of global warming an 
appropriate balance 
we need a better understanding of the economic and social 
implications of dealing with global warming said lambrix 
