weeks 
on tuesday however kohl called for immediate talks with east 
germany on a monetary union between the two states to try to 
rescue east germanys crumbling economy and stop the growing exodus 
several state governments have proposed curbing the massive 
financial assistance paid to the east german resettlers and the 
ethnic german newcomers 
