said that requires us to declare an unusual event we do a plant 
walkdown and make sure there was no damage of any kind 
diablo canyons accelerometer which measures the force exerted 
by earthquakes detected quakecaused motion equal to only one 
fivehundredth the force of gravity thomas said 
the richter scale is an indirect gauge of the energy released by 
an earthquake as measured by the ground motion recorded on a 
seismograph an earthquake of 35 on the richter scale can cause 
slight damage in the local area while 4 can cause moderate damage 
