air quality standards the compromise however exempts smaller 
polluters by raising the cutoff for emission levels 
in addition there is agreement that the bill would contain no 
requirement for automakers to produce or sell alternativefuel 
automobiles chafee and other senators had hoped to insert such a 
requirement on the senate floor 
