initiative against gangs patrolling schools and parks removing 
graffiti and befriending neighborhood youth the group recently 
formed its fourth los angeles chapter 
theres no way we can claim any kind of success because the 
homicides are still there said valdivia whose agency works with 
100 men plus but the signs are there 
