probably accept the post if the front wins the election and he is 
asked by a majority of the movement 
the front on jan 23 reversed its pledge to stay out of the 
election it has refused to become a political party choosing 
instead to remain a political movement 
iliescu went to the central tribunal to officially register the 
front which has split from the government and the eightmember 
ruling council 
