reported that aouns tanks chased the militiamen to the edge of the 
dog river valley 
other tank units hammered the militias besieged kassardjian 
garrison in the east beirut district of ein rummaneh all day 
tuesday in apparent preparation to storm it police reported 
according to aouns command all escape routes from 
